{"id":"01hvn2rm65ax494f5512k64k0s","add_time_ms":1713325756613,"type":"doc","title":"页面处理函数-下拉刷新","_id":"142","char_count":{"word":112,"char_without_spaces":152,"char_with_spaces":152,"char_all":156},"content":"下来刷新是小程序中常见的一种刷新方式，当用户下拉页面时，页面会自动刷新，以便用户获取最新的内容。\n\n小程序中实现上拉加载更多的方式：\n1.在app.json或者page.json中开启允许下拉，同时可以配置窗口，loading样式等。\n2.在页面js中定义onPullDownRefresh事件监听用户下拉刷新。","edit_time_ms":1713327362178,"snapshots":[{"id":"01jdc8smcs14sjrbdgsevh2a0t","item_id":"01hvn2rm65ax494f5512k64k0s","add_time_ms":1732357443994,"hash":"2295661a52f0f557694c0e503f0c8242","length":156,"char_count_char_with_spaces":152,"char_count_char_without_spaces":152,"char_count_word":112,"version_key":1}]}